OL,4,C The Chief Judge, Jellybean Jessica,   
OL,5,C has approved the issuance of a        
OL,6,C temporary Gold Loyalty Pass for the   
OL,7,C US President's delegation.            
OL,9,F The award ceremony will take place at 
OL,10,F the Barvikha Research Nexus. Attendees
OL,11,F will be served a special commemorative
OL,12,F green borscht and unlimited kefir.    
OL,14,F SABRE payment systems will have a     
OL,15,F face-recognition option to toast his  
OL,16,F health.                              F
